                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8749" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0268</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1377 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">外卖行业的“青山计划”—美团的特色低碳之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The &quot;Green Mountain Plan&quot; of the takeout industry—Meituan&#39;s characteristic low-carbon path</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李振华，周子龙</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京三快科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">环保部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色低碳经济；美团；青山计划；外卖行业；平台型企业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Green and low-carbon economy; Meituan Qingshan Plan; The food delivery industry; Platform based enterprises;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">外卖行业的飞速发展给消费者带来生活便利的同时也带来了外卖包装等废弃物污染，成为人们美好生活的双刃剑。国家对低碳经济的布局以及相关政策的发布，使绿色低碳建设成为热议话题。为了承担社会责任，美团发布青山计划，围绕自身核心业务开展特色绿色低碳建设，并最终形成了绿色包装供应链建设、青山科技、“商家-平台-消费者”可持续生态圈以及青山公益这四大特色板块。本案例对美团青山计划的开展过程进行了详细描述，旨在帮助学员更好了解绿色低碳经济内涵，引导学员思考平台型企业如何开展绿色低碳建设，进而承担社会责任。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The rapid development of the food delivery industry has brought convenience to consumers, but it has also brought pollution from food packaging and other waste, becoming a double-edged sword for people&#39;s better lives. The country&#39;s layout of low-carbon economy and the release of relevant policies have made green and low-carbon construction a hot topic of discussion. In order to assume social responsibility, Meituan has launched the Qingshan Plan, focusing on its core business to carry out characteristic green and low-carbon construction, and ultimately formed four characteristic sectors: green packaging supply chain construction, Qingshan Technology, &quot;merchant - platform - consumer&quot; sustainable ecosystem, and Qingshan Public Welfare. This case provides a detailed description of the implementation process of the Meituan Qingshan Plan, aiming to help students better understand the connotation of green and low-carbon economy, and guide students to think about how platform based enterprises can carry out green and low-carbon construction, and thus assume social responsibility.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《环境会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">低碳经济；可持续发展理论；利益相关者理论；绿色技术创新理论；平台型企业；平台型企业社会责任；战略性企业社会责任；外部性理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
